body_text:
TF_ExtendGraph can only add ops to an existing graph (by design, hence the name).  If you modify existing ops in the graphdef which has been used in a session this will have no effect.
The only way I know to achieve this is to make a new session using the modified graph.
@mrry  Is this correct?

